videos.description: Christ Koumadje scores the first 6 points for Florida State, capping it off with a putback dunk to put them ahead.
videos.headline: Koumadje keeps carrying FSU with putback dunk

videos.description: Chirst Koumadje throws in the putback dunk to tie the game at 34-34 as the halftime buzzer sounds.
videos.headline: Koumadje ties it as 1st-half buzzer expires
